dct_title_s: The Rand-McNally new library atlas map of Union of South Africa, Basutoland and Swaziland
dct_description_sm: At top of map: Library atlas of the world. [Union of South Africa, Basutoland, and Swaziland.]. 93-94. Relief shown by hachures. Inset: Rhodesia and Portuguese East Africa. From: The library atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1912.
